Package au.csiro.pathling.terminology

Interface TerminologyParameters

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
LookupParameters, SubsumesParameters, TranslateParameters, ValidateCodeParameters
public interface TerminologyParameters extends Serializable
Represents parameters that are passed to a terminology operation.

Must be Serializable so that it can be used as a cache key.

Author:
John Grimes
